{
  "id": "cc3ba05f17884c42aa8b5cdd0c9ddc74",
  "title": "Easy Drag and Drop Inventory System",
  "description": "A drag and drop system easy to understand and brings more depth to your games.",
  "longDescription": "<p>This is a simple drag and drop inventory system that is easy to understand and brings more depth to your games.</p><p>This pack comprises an example drag and drop inventory using three item types (Weapon, Armor, Utility) so you can see how it works and make it work in your projects.</p><p>It contains the ability to collect and store items in your inventory using a drag and drop system to interact with them including equipping items or discarding them back into the world.</p><p><br /></p><p>Some of the assets (The sword and Torch) have been provided by Epic Games Content.</p><p><br /></p><p>Update : Because of the UMG Plugin for Controller input, this project does not work on UE5</p>",
  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><ul><li>The system is made for modularity and universal capabilities.</li><li> Collect Item types to add to your inventory.</li><li>Equip Items in your inventory using Drag and Drop.</li><li>Filter your item types.</li><li>Throw items out of your inventory back into the world.</li><li> Tooltip UI features a 3D widget and a UI on your inventory.</li></ul><p>Number of Blueprints: 16</p><p>Input: Gamepad, Keyboard, Mouse</p><p>Network Replicated: No</p><p>Supported Development Platforms:</p><p>Windows: Yes</p><p>Mac: No</p><p>Documentation: All blueprints have been appropriately commented to explain how they work.</p><p><br /></p><p>Additional documenation: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1UCtZTrUZi5JUYOLbN5tRYjLjDhulKU1q3YrO7N1BT4M/edit?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1UCtZTrUZi5JUYOLbN5tRYjLjDhulKU1q3YrO7N1BT4M/edit?usp&#61;sharing</a></p><p><br /></p><p>For any issues please email me at lukedodds94&#64;gmail.com with the subject &#34;Drag and Drop&#34;</p><p>Important/Additional Notes:</p>",
